OL,3,CThe light bulb moment that led one
OL,4,Cwoman to give a helping hand
OL,6,F"That is what it's all about. That's
OL,7,Fwhat we do and it's ordinary people
OL,8,Fdoing this. We don't have any riches
OL,9,Fcoming in. This is ordinary people
OL,10,Fjust donating a pound, two pounds,
OL,11,Fthings like that", she told UTV.
OL,13,FThe people who also support Help is At
OL,14,FHand are people who know what it's
OL,15,Flike to be under the poverty line.
OL,17,FLouise talks about a doctor's wife who
OL,18,Fcame in to donate.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
