OL,3,CThe light bulb moment that led one
OL,4,Cwoman to give a helping hand
OL,6,F"She said 'I know you're looking at me
OL,7,Fnow but I come from the poorest
OL,8,Fbackground that you could imagine. I
OL,9,Fknow what this is like but I've never
OL,10,Fseen anything like what we're seeing
OL,11,Fnow.'"
OL,13,FLouise agrees. She feels things have
OL,14,Fnever been as bad.
OL,16,FI ask her what living in poverty in
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland in 2025 looks like.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
