OL,3,CThe light bulb moment that led one
OL,4,Cwoman to give a helping hand
OL,6,FShe said: "It's a lack of food. It's
OL,7,Fthe lack of heat. Footwear. I know
OL,8,Finstantly when I look down at
OL,9,Fsomebody's feet that they have
OL,10,Fnothing. At the beginning I couldn't
OL,11,Ftell that but now, when I look at a
OL,12,Fmum or a dad, I know by their shoes
OL,13,Fthat they have nothing.
OL,15,F"Maybe they have holes in the side,
OL,16,Fthings like that. People come in
OL,17,Flooking for shoes for their kids
OL,18,Fbecause their shoes are too small and
OL,19,Fare crushing their feet. Is this it?
OL,20,FIs this what we've come to?"
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
