OL,3,CThe light bulb moment that led one
OL,4,Cwoman to give a helping hand
OL,6,FThe cost of rent is another reason
OL,7,Fpeople are struggling.
OL,9,F"The rents are high. It's ridiculous
OL,10,Fsome of the people we go out to and
OL,11,Fthey show us what they're paying in
OL,12,Frent.
OL,14,F"We were out with a family last week.
OL,15,FThe girl's and part of the husband's
OL,16,Fwage went on the rent so how can they
OL,17,Flive?...Is it that nobody cares.
OL,18,FThat's what it feels like. The
OL,19,Fordinary people are being forgotten."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
