OL,3,CThe light bulb moment that led one
OL,4,Cwoman to give a helping hand
OL,6,FChristmas is expensive for everyone.
OL,7,FFamilies under the poverty line
OL,8,Fdoubtless struggle but Louise says
OL,9,Fthere's even been a shift in what
OL,10,Ffamilies are looking for between last
OL,11,FChristmas and this one.
OL,13,F"People I notice this year, even more
OL,14,Fthan last year, they're asking for
OL,15,Fthings for their kids for Christmas
OL,16,Fbut they are more interested in having
OL,17,Ffood for Christmas Day.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
