OL,3,CThe light bulb moment that led one
OL,4,Cwoman to give a helping hand
OL,6,F"I didn't even see that as much last
OL,7,Fyear. People asking for a wee
OL,8,Fhamper... People are saying that they
OL,9,Fdon't mind if it's just a wee car for
OL,10,Fthe little one, they just want to be
OL,11,Fable to give them Christmas
OL,12,FDinner...to me that's horrible. It
OL,13,Freally is. It shouldn't be happening."
OL,15,FDespite the harrowing situations that
OL,16,FHelp Is At Hand witnesses and deals
OL,17,Fwith, Louise is unrepentant about
OL,18,Fdedicating her time to this work.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
