OL,3,CThe light bulb moment that led one
OL,4,Cwoman to give a helping hand
OL,6,F"It's the most satisfying thing I've
OL,7,Fever done apart from being a
OL,8,Fmum....We're here for such a short
OL,9,Ftime. If we can do anything to help
OL,10,Fsomebody, a child or an elderly
OL,11,Fperson, that's the main thing.
OL,13,F"People are under the misconception
OL,14,Fthat everybody who's poor is a drug
OL,15,Faddict. Everybody who's poor is an
OL,16,Falcoholic.
OL,18,F"It's not the case. There are plenty
OL,19,Fof hard-working people out there, lots
OL,20,Fof them who are struggling," she
OL,21,Fstressed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
